  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      637.53,
      501.04,
      664.61
    ],
    "text": "Two Suspects Arrested for Handling Financial Transactions Linked to Organized Crime Gangs \u2013 Negombo Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      679.17,
      516.58,
      720.05
    ],
    "text": "On 15.02.2026, officers of the Negombo Police Station arrested a suspect for possession of heroin. The suspect is currently being detained under detention orders, and investigations are ongoing.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      734.51,
      523.89,
      789.19
    ],
    "text": "Based on information obtained from the suspect during the investigation, further inquiries were carried out using details related to a bank account number connected to the case. Through the examination of CCTV footage, investigators identified individuals withdrawing money from the relevant account.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      89.3,
      160.0,
      407.7,
      180.47
    ],
    "text": "D/Media/Out/385/2026 2026.03.04 \u0dd0\u0dba 0810",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      45.47,
      496.44,
      86.37
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, on 03.03.2026, two suspects were apprehended in Colombo by the investigating officers while in possession of Rs. 3.3 million, which had been withdrawn from the said personal bank account.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      100.93,
      519.46,
      128.01
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspects are 21 and 26 years old and are residents of Aduruppu Veediya and Colombo 14.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      142.45,
      517.27,
      197.13
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that these two individuals were involved in depositing and withdrawing funds through several bank accounts in Colombo on behalf of members of organized crime groups and drug trafficking networks who are currently operating from overseas.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      211.69,
      474.1,
      224.97
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being carried out by the Negombo Police Station.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      239.06,
      530.37,
      382.03
    ],
    "text": "02. \u0db8\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc2\u0dba \u0d9d\u0ddc\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0da7 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0dca\u200d \u0dc3\u0dd0 \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca 06 \u0db4\u0daf\u0db4\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dd9\u0da7 - \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dc1\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba \u0db6\u0dbd \u0ddc \u0da2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0db1\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0db4 \u0ddd\u0da7\u0dca\u0db4\u0da7\u0dca \u0db3\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbb. 2026.02.27 \u0dd9\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca\u0dca \u0ddc\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dd9\u0dc3\u0db4\u0db8\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dd9\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d9d\u0ddc\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db4\u0db8\u0dca \u0d85 \u0dbb\u0ddc\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0db4\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca\u0dca \u0ddc\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dba \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc1\u0db1 \u0dab\u0da9\u0ddc\u0dba\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0d9f\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc1\u0db1 \u0d86\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dca\u0db7 \u0dbb \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd2.",
