  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      539.75,
      505.48,
      570.24
    ],
    "text": "06 Suspects Arrested in Connection with a Murder \u2013 Police Special Task Force Jayawardenapura Kotte Camp",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      584.73,
      495.93,
      625.61
    ],
    "text": "On 27.02.2026, several investigation teams, including officers of the Grandpass Police Station, initiated investigations into the murder of a person who had been assaulted with sharp weapons within the Grandpass Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      640.05,
      525.97,
      708.53
    ],
    "text": "Based on information received during the investigation, officers of the Police Special Task Force Jayawardenapura Kotte Camp apprehended five suspects directly involved in the murder and one suspect for aiding and abetting the offenders on 03.03.2026. The suspects were subsequently handed over to the Grandpass Police Station for further legal proceedings.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      723.09,
      499.9,
      750.19
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspects are between 21 and 31 years of age and are residents of the Wellampitiya, Orugodawatte, and Dematagoda areas.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      764.75,
      437.98,
      778.03
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Grandpass Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      44.97,
      530.41,
      156.28
    ],
    "text": "03. \u0db8\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc2\u0dba \u0d9d\u0ddc\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0da7 \u0d85\u0dd9\u0dc1\u0dba \u0dbb \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd0 \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dd9\u0da7 - \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dba \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dba 2026.01.16 \u0dd9\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dba \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dd9\u0dc3\u0db4\u0db8\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dd9\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d9d\u0ddc\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db4\u0db8\u0dca \u0d85 \u0dbb\u0ddc\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0db4\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dba \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dba \u0db8\u0d9f\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc1\u0db1 \u0d86\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dca\u0db7 \u0dbb \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd2.",
    "fonts": [
