    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      358.84,
      521.03,
      399.72
    ],
    "text": "On 16.01.2026, officers of the Mahiyanganaya Police commenced investigations into the murder of a person who had been attacked with a sharp weapon within the Mahiyanganaya Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      414.3,
      524.49,
      455.18
    ],
    "text": "Based on information received by the investigating officers, a suspect connected to the above crime was arrested in the Arawatta area of Mahiyanganaya on the afternoon of 03.03.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      469.62,
      473.98,
      482.9
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspect is a 16-year-old resident of Arawatta, Mahiyanganaya.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      497.46,
      496.79,
      524.54
    ],
    "text": "In connection with this incident, eight suspects had previously been arrested and produced before the Honorable Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
